df-probes-footage-of-unarmed-palestinians-struck-from-the-air-killed-in-gaza/0000018e-6a00-dfa8-a98e-6f098aa00000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸定居者犹太领袖涉嫌计划破坏巴勒斯坦人的财产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/head-of-west-bank-settler-yeshiva-suspected-of-planning-to-damage-palestinians-property/0000018e-66d9-df1f-a3cf-e6fba96c0000</link><description>拉比约瑟夫·埃利祖尔（Rabbi Yosef Elitzur）被视为定居点激进右翼活动人士的精神领袖之一，因他的学生涉嫌犯下的暴力罪行而受到警方讯问</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 08:09:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/head-of-west-bank-settler-yeshiva-suspected-of-planning-to-damage-palestinians-property/0000018e-66d9-df1f-a3cf-e6fba96c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉布林肯，美国无法阻止以色列的拉法攻势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/u-s-cant-stop-israels-rafah-offensive-netanyahu-tells-blinken/0000018e-6762-d1c9-af8f-6febea9a0000</link><description>总理表示，他告诉美国国务卿，如有必要，以色列将“单独行动”，因为布林肯表示，入侵将进一步在国际上孤立以色列</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 05:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article/.premium/u-s-cant-stop-israels-rafah-offensive-netanyahu-tells-blinken/0000018e-6762-d1c9-af8f-6febea9a0000</guid></item><item><title>如何说服士兵重返战场？对以色列国防军即将离任的心理健康负责人的采访</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-do-you-convince-soldiers-to-return-to-battle-idf-mental-health-chief-explains/0000018e-695d-d477-abbf-ef5dcb1d0000</link><description>以色列国防军心理健康部门负责人及其一系列治疗单位正在应对军队自 1973 年以来面临的最大心理危机。但是，卢西恩·塔萨-劳尔博士表示，如果士兵们有足够的勇气去战斗，“他们就赢了”回家后不会崩溃&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 04:47:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-do-you-convince-soldiers-to-return-to-battle-idf-mental-health-chief-explains/0000018e-695d-d477-abbf-ef5dcb1d0000</guid></item><item><ti